      "description": "Affordable, straightforward, and full of potential, this vehicle is a practical choice for someone looking for dependable basic transportation at a budget-friendly price. It shows its age and is best suited for a buyer who values value over perfection, but it still offers a comfortable cabin, useful everyday functionality, and an opportunity to own a vehicle without stretching your budget. A sensible option for commuting, a second car, or a handy project.",
