    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Looking for an affordable set of wheels or a solid little project? This car isn\u2019t perfect, but it\u2019s a great budget-friendly option for someone handy or anyone who just needs basic transportation without spending a fortune. It\u2019s got the kind of honest, well-used character you\u2019d expect at this price, and with a bit of TLC it could be a really worthwhile buy. Priced to move and ideal for a fixer-upper, parts donor, or cheap runabout.",
      "price": 4500.0,
